file: RunLockManager.php
class: "Ineersa\\AgentCore\\Application\\Handler\\RunLockManager"
type: readonly final class
summary: "The RunLockManager provides a mechanism to execute critical sections of code exclusively for a specific run ID using distributed locking. It leverages a LockFactory to acquire locks with a configurable time-to-live, ensuring thread-safe or process-safe execution of run-specific logic."
